Apache NiFi is an easy to use, powerful, reliable system to process and distribute the data.

NiFi Features: Apache NiFi supports powerful and scalable directed graphs of data routing, transformation, and system mediation logic. The following are some of the capabilities and Objectives of Apache NiFi.
	1. Web based user interface
		seamless experience between design, control, feedback and monitoring
	2. Highly configurable
		Loss tolerant vs guaranteed delivery
		Low latency vs high throughput
		Dynamic prioritization
		Flow can be modified at runtime
		Back pressure
	3. Data Provenance
		Tracked dataflow from beginning to end
	4. Designed for extension
		Build your own processors and more
		Enables rapid development and effective testing
	5. Secure
		SSL, SSH, HTTPS, and encrypted content etc...
		Multi-tenant authorization and internal authorization/policy management
